<div class="hero-image">
  <div class="overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero-text">
    <h1>Welcome Hikers!</h1>
    <p>Are you looking for a trail in the middle of Utah that will take 3 days to complete? Or maybe you want to go on a
      quick trail after work! No matter what type of hike you’re planning, we can help you find the best trails matching
      your preferences with an expansive 7 day weather forecast to adequately plan any type of hike. Don’t get rained
      out half way through a hike, use our technology to have as much fun as possible.</p>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal">Sign
      up-it's free</button>
  </div>
